<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans von Aulenbach, Amtmann zu Schweinberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt Unkenntnis über seinen angeblichen Kundschafter Fritz Wiese mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_457" id="227v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_457_r1l30">Hanſen von Vlnbach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l31">Amptman cʒu <expan>Sweÿnb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_457_r1l32"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von eins wegen genant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l33">fricʒ vvyſe vvie der 
<del rend="strikethrough">bey ew danyden cʒu lande </del> beleument vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l34">gecʒigen ſey worden . daʒ Er vns bey euch danyden cʒulande </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l35">kuntſchaft verſpehe / . dauon vviſſen vvir nihtʒ vnd <expan>kenne<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l36">auch des <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> fricʒen vvyſen niht / Vnd wo vvir euch <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l37">vvıllen beweiſen möhten das teten vvir gern . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_457_r1l38"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>do<ex>min</ex>ic<ex>am</ex></expan> <expan>Trinitat<ex>em</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_457" id="227v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen von Ulnbach, amptman czu <expan>Sweynb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von eins wegen genant Fricz
                        Wyse, wie der beleument und geczigen sey worden, daz er uns bey euch danyden
                        czulande kuntschaft verspehe, davon wissen wir nihcz und
                                <expan>kenne<ex>n</ex></expan> auch des
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Friczen Wysen niht. Und wo wir euch
                                <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> willen beweisen möhten, das teten wir
                        gern. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ic<ex>am</ex></expan>
<expan>trinitat<ex>em</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
